{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "e7b5f4a1-4f2a-4a8a-b8b8-8a8a8a8a8a8a",
    "name": "通用审批基础服务",
    "description": "# 请假审批流程测试集\n\n本测试集包含三个测试场景：\n\n## 1. 普通审批流程（9步）\n测试完整的请假审批流程，包括直接主管审批和HR审批。\n\n## 2. 任务转交流程（10步）\n测试任务转交功能，manager1将任务转交给manager2代为审批。\n\n## 3. 任务退回流程（6步）\n测试任务被拒绝的场景，直接主管拒绝后流程结束。\n\n---\n\n## 全局变量说明\n\n### 普通流程变量\n- `businessKey`: 业务键（格式：LEAVE_ + 时间戳）\n- `processInstanceId`: 流程实例ID\n- `directManagerTaskId`: 直接主管任务ID\n- `hrTaskId`: HR任务ID\n\n### 转交流程变量\n- `delegateBusinessKey`: 转交场景业务键（格式：DELEGATE_ + 时间戳）\n- `delegateProcessInstanceId`: 转交场景流程实例ID\n- `delegateOriginalTaskId`: 转交前任务ID（manager1）\n- `delegateNewTaskId`: 转交后任务ID（manager2）\n- `delegateHrTaskId`: 转交场景HR任务ID\n\n### 退回流程变量\n- `rollbackBusinessKey`: 退回场景业务键（格式：ROLLBACK_ + 时间戳）\n- `rollbackProcessInstanceId`: 退回场景流程实例ID\n- `rollbackDirectManagerTaskId`: 退回场景直接主管任务ID\n\n---\n\n## 接口说明\n\n### 模板接口\n- `GET /api/approval/template` - 获取模板列表\n- `POST /api/approval/template/{templateCode}/deploy` - 部署模板\n\n### 流程接口\n- `POST /api/approval/process` - 启动流程\n- `GET /api/approval/process/{processInstanceId}/variables` - 获取流程变量\n\n### 任务接口\n- `GET /api/approval/task?assignee={user}` - 获取用户任务列表\n- `POST /api/approval/task/{taskId}` - 完成任务\n- `POST /api/approval/task/{taskId}/delegate` - 转交任务\n\n### 历史接口\n- `GET /api/approval/history/log?businessKey={businessKey}` - 查询审批历史",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "普通审批流程",
      "description": "## 普通审批流程\n\n测试场景：员工提交3天请假申请，直接主管和HR依次审批通过。\n\n### 流程说明\n1. 员工提交请假申请（3天）\n2. 直接主管（manager1）审批同意\n3. HR（hr1）审批同意\n4. 流程结束\n\n### 重要说明\n**必须完整运行此文件夹（右键 -> Run folder），不能单独运行某个步骤！**\n因为变量需要在前面的步骤中保存到全局变量中。",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// 清除普通审批流程的全局变量",
              "pm.globals.unset('businessKey');",
              "pm.globals.unset('processInstanceId');",
              "pm.globals.unset('directManagerTaskId');",
              "pm.globals.unset('hrTaskId');",
              "console.log('已清除普通审批流程的全局变量');",
              ""
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. 获取模板列表",
          "description": "### 获取模板列表\n\n获取系统中所有已创建的审批模板，检查LEAVE_001请假审批模板是否存在。\n\n**接口**: `GET /api/approval/template`\n\n**预期结果**: 返回包含LEAVE_001模板的列表",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/approval/template",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "approval", "template"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. 部署LEAVE_001模板",
          "description": "### 部署LEAVE_001模板\n\n将LEAVE_001请假审批模板部署到Flowable流程引擎，生成可执行的流程定义。\n\n**接口**: `POST /api/approval/template/LEAVE_001/deploy`\n\n**预期结果**: 模板部署成功，状态变为DEPLOYED",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/approval/template/LEAVE_001/deploy",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "approval", "template", "LEAVE_001", "deploy"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. 启动请假流程",
          "description": "### 启动请假流程\n\n启动一个3天请假审批流程，传递审批人变量。\n\n**接口**: `POST /api/approval/process`\n\n**请求体**:\n```json\n{\n  \"templateCode\": \"LEAVE_001\",\n  \"businessKey\": \"{{businessKey}}\",\n  \"variables\": {\n    \"leave_days\": 3,\n    \"direct_manager\": \"manager1\",\n    \"senior_manager\": \"director1\",\n    \"hr\": \"hr1\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**变量说明**:\n- `leave_days`: 请假天数（3天≤3天，走简短流程）\n- `direct_manager`: 直接主管（manager1）\n- `senior_manager`: 上级主管（director1）\n- `hr`: 人事（hr1）\n\n**自动保存**: businessKey, processInstanceId 到全局变量",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// 在发送请求前生成唯一的业务键",
                  "const businessKey = 'LEAVE_' + new Date().getTime();",
                  "pm.globals.set('businessKey', businessKey);",
                  "console.log('生成本次业务键:', businessKey);",
                  ""
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "console.log('步骤3响应:', pm.response.text());",
                  "const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (response.code === 200 && response.data) {",
                  "    pm.globals.set('processInstanceId', response.data);",
                  "    console.log('已保存processInstanceId:', response.data);",
                  "    console.log('businessKey:', pm.globals.get('businessKey'));",
                  "}",
                  ""
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"templateCode\": \"LEAVE_001\",\n  \"businessKey\": \"{{businessKey}}\",\n  \"variables\": {\n    \"leave_days\": 3,\n    \"direct_manager\": \"manager1\",\n    \"senior_manager\": \"director1\",\n    \"hr\": \"hr1\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/approval/process",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "approval", "process"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. 获取直接主管任务",
          "description": "### 获取直接主管任务\n\n查询直接主管（manager1）的待处理任务，获取刚才启动的请假审批任务。\n\n**接口**: `GET /api/approval/task?assignee=manager1`\n\n**预期结果**: 返回manager1的待处理任务列表，包含刚刚创建的直接主管审批任务\n\n**自动保存**: directManagerTaskId 到全局变量",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "console.log('步骤4响应:', JSON.stringify(response).substring(0, 200));",
                  "if (response.code === 200 && response.data && response.data.length > 0) {",
                  "    const processInstanceId = pm.globals.get('processInstanceId');",
                  "    console.log('当前processInstanceId:', processInstanceId);",
                  "    const task = response.data.find(t => t.processInstanceId === processInstanceId);",
                  "    const taskId = task ? task.id : response.data[0].id;",
                  "    pm.globals.set('directManagerTaskId', taskId);",
                  "    console.log('已保存directManagerTaskId:', taskId);",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('没有找到manager1的待处理任务');",
                  "}",
                  ""
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/approval/task?assignee=manager1",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "approval", "task"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "assignee",
                  "value": "manager1"
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5. 获取流程变量",
          "description": "### 获取流程变量\n\n在流程结束前获取当前流程的变量信息，验证传递的参数是否正确。\n\n**注意**: 此步骤会使用businessKey获取最新的流程实例ID\n\n**接口**: `GET /api/approval/process/{processInstanceId}/variables`\n\n**预期结果**: 返回流程变量，包含：\n- leave_days: 3\n- direct_manager: manager1\n- senior_manager: director1\n- hr: hr1",
          "event": [
